create filename.mgc then add the following lines into it

#!/bin/bash
0 string FILENAME Filename data
!:mime Filename

eg:

#!/bin/bash
0 string ALFRED Alfred data
!:mime Alfred


Then on Ur terminal run

 file -C -m filename.mgc
 to convert to magic file

After that run 
chmod u+x school.mgc 
to execute the file 

then run
cp /bin/ls .
ls -la
file --mime-type -m filename.mgc *
file -m filename.mgc *


Then you  add, commit and push